		<title>聯準會放鬆貨幣政策後，美國股市創下歷史新高</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/us-stocks-hit-record-highs-after-federal-reserve-easing</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 01:47:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市場新聞及觀點]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Indices]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[S&P 500]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[SP500]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[最近的新聞]]></category>
